{
  "id": "adv_event_2401_01_03",
  "title": "渚と\n大事な\nペンダント",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一方その頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Meanwhile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.0666666746,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "沙季と芽衣が大掃除をしていた時、渚は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While Saki and Mei were cleaning‚ Nagisa was――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.0666666746,
      "endTime": 3.1999997377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ……このカゴの中身を見たら\nみんなびっくりするだろうなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… Everyone will be so surprised\nwhen they see what's inside this basket.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0666665316,
      "endTime": 10.8666665316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "猫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Cat",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "にゃ～ん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meow~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0634466728,
      "endTime": 12.556779881399999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "もうちょっとだけ我慢してね\n寮に着いたらカゴから出してあげるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just be patient for a little while longer.\nI’ll let you out of the basket when we get back to the dorm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7634465457,
      "endTime": 17.9756236316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "「旅行に行くから飼ってる猫を預かってほしい」って\n友達から頼まれた時はびっくりしたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised when my friend asked me\nto look after her cat while she’s away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1724037728,
      "endTime": 24.900000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに可愛いんだもん\nきっとみんなも喜ぶだろうな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s so cute.\nI’m sure everyone will be happy~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0645577354,
      "endTime": 31.2396368904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――渚の妄想",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Nagisa's imagination.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2364170316,
      "endTime": 33.376417065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うわ～、猫にゃんだ～！\nこんにちは～、芽衣にゃんだよ～、にゃんにゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ a kitty!\nHello~‚ I’m Mei-nyan~‚ meow meow~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2697518908,
      "endTime": 42.2320872867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ばかりずるいですわよ、私にも抱かせなさい\nきゃっ！　この子、私に猫ぱんちしましたわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not fair that only Mei gets to cuddle it. Let me give it a cuddle too.\nKyaa! This little one just gave me a cat punch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4288674279,
      "endTime": 52.4151944085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "猫のしつけは任せて下さい\nエサやりからトイレまで、完璧に管理してみせます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave the cat training to me.\nI’ll manage everything perfectly‚ from feeding to cleaning the litter box.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6288674279,
      "endTime": 58.995420543799995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "うふふ……もふもふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe… So fluffy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1955340945,
      "endTime": 65.23208728659999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……もふもふする琴乃ちゃん、可愛い……\nこの子を見てみんながどんな反応するか、楽しみだなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh… Kotono-chan petting the kitty is so cute…\nI can’t wait to see everyone’s reaction when they see this little one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.4955330773,
      "endTime": 78.9112023278,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13037.800256000011
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま～。……あれ？　リビングから音が聞こえる\n誰かテレビでも見てるのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m back~. …Huh? I hear something coming from the living room.\nIs someone watching TV?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.207982469,
      "endTime": 90.68655417000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "猫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Cat",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "にゃ～ん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meow~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8833343112,
      "endTime": 92.309999963,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　どうしたの？　お腹空いたのかな？\nそう言えばキャットフードを買うお金を預かってたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm? What’s wrong? Are you hungry?\nNow that I think about it‚ I got some money to buy cat food.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5166666273,
      "endTime": 101.80859377419999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "他に必要なものもあるから今のうちに買ってこようかな\n猫ちゃん、すぐ戻るから大人しく待っててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to buy something else too‚ so maybe it would be better to go shopping now.\nI’ll be right back‚ kitty‚ so wait here quietly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0053739154,
      "endTime": 110.7707936847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "猫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Cat",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "にゃーん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meow~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.967573826,
      "endTime": 112.2275753543,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.4842420185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "キャットフード、トイレの砂、水飲み用の食器……\n後買い忘れたものはないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cat food‚ cat litter and water bowl…\nI didn’t forget to buy anything else‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5342420185,
      "endTime": 123.16666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "猫用のおもちゃもあった方がいいのかな？\nでも芽衣ちゃんが沢山持ってそうな気がするんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if I should get a cat toy too?\nBut I have a feeling Mei-chan has a lot of toys.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.3572150157,
      "endTime": 131.1228383945,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7442.784984300005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12409.454194099993
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.2333358765
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "あ、電話だ。相手は……琴乃ちゃん？\nもしもし、琴乃ちゃん。明けましておめでとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ it’s a phone call. It's from… Kotono-chan?\nHello‚ Kotono-chan. Happy New Year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7333368938,
      "endTime": 141.37333704649998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.7137208218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "明けましておめでとう、渚\n今年もよろしくね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy New Year‚ Nagisa.\nLet's have a nice year",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.5564079848,
      "endTime": 145.779491767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそ、よろしくね\n琴乃ちゃんは今、実家だよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Same to you‚ thank you.\nYou’re at your parents’ house now‚ right‚ Kotono-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9897413182,
      "endTime": 151.4591973233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.6559774645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。渚は寮だったよね？\nちょっと頼みがあるんだけど、いいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. You’re at the dorm‚ Nagisa?\nI have a favor to ask. Would that be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6559774645,
      "endTime": 159.17219069080002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "実は、寮のリビングに大切なペンダントを\n置きっぱなしにしてたことを思い出したの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I just remembered that I left an important pendant\nin the dorm living room…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.3559774645,
      "endTime": 165.427088476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "すぐにでも取りに戻りたいんだけど\nこの後、急な仕事が入っちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to go back and get it right away‚\nbut I have some urgent work to do after this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6226441312,
      "endTime": 171.7266349721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.9226441312
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2401_01_03-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、琴乃ちゃんのお気に入りのペンダント？\n麻奈さんからもらったっていう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean your favorite pendant‚ Kotono-chan?\nThe one Mana-san gave you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.9226441312,
      "endTime": 178.2094467093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
